{"article_id":"DnEzBrItSDeExDWH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Facebook denies censoring conservative stories from trending topics","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"There ' s a conceit","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that says","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"everything at Facebook is run by data , not people .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"And we prefer it that way .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"For the site ' s billion users , believing","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"there ' s no human puppet master behind the scenes","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"makes its growing control over life more palatable .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"It ' s just a clever machine ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"reflecting our desires better and better with every interaction ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"right ?","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"For news producers , we have to believe","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that the platform treats everyone equally :","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that it ' s a publisher not an editor .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"A conservative whistleblower at Facebook yesterday claimed in a report","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"that the influential \" trending news \" tab was deliberately biased toward liberal news","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"- something","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"the social network denies .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" I ' d come on shift","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and I ' d discover","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that CPAC","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"[ Conservative Political Action Conference ]","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"or Mitt Romney or Glenn Beck or popular conservative topics wouldn ' t be trending","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"because either the curator didn ' t recognize the news topic","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"or it was like they had a bias against Ted Cruz , \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"the former news curator told the tech blog Gizmodo .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Silicon Valley loves using the word algorithm","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"to cover the word judgment ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"but any platform","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"built by humans","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"is always political .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"The engineers","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"building the products","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"want to skew them toward \" quality \" content ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"but it ' s hard to determine what quality is , exactly ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"without making a choice","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"influenced by values .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"When I read suggestions","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that Facebook might be skewing its trending bar ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"my first reaction , as a San Francisco liberal , was to be slightly pleased","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"( any help","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"we can get against Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"right ? ) .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"But what if the tables were turned ?","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"\" I wonder what the psychological effects of it are , \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"said Vince Coglianese , editor of the conservative news site The Daily Caller .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" Millions of Facebook users now have no idea","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"that the things","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"they ' re concerned about","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"are the concerns of a lot of people .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"It ' s scary to think","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Facebook ' s intentionally isolating vast swaths of the country . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Facebook reveals news feed experiment","depth":3},{"id":54,"text":"to control emotions","depth":3},{"id":55,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":56,"text":"Facebook ' s in a tricky spot","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"because curation is necessary .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Truly viral news content tends to be terrible .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"The front page of Reddit ' s ' \" hot \" section , an imperfect but useful barometer for the viral stories of the day , currently has headlines like :","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"\" Chameleon unsure bug is food or not \"","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"and \" These condoms are around 60 years old .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"( found in my basement ) \" .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Meanwhile my Facebook trending bar has :","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" Federal Trade Commission :","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Judge Rules Against Agency ' s Bid","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"to Block Health Care Systems Merger \" .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"It ' s probably fair to assume that the FTC news was not going as viral as that old condom ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"but a Facebook employee decided","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"it was more important .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Facebook is the dominant player in the media today .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"As news websites lose relevance to readers","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who find content socially ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"and as stories are published directly onto Facebook as Instant articles ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the company ' s power will only grow .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"To turn Facebook ' s trending bar into a Reddit page is not the answer .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"But Facebook has to be more honest about how it operates as an editor .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"\" Just be transparent about how the words on the screen are getting there , \"","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Coglianese said .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"If there ' s one thing","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Silicon Valley loves more than the conceit of an amoral algorithm ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"it is secrecy .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"And as a social network with a newsfeed of vacation pictures , Facebook could get away with being secretive about their curation .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"As the most powerful publisher and now editor in the world today , Facebook owes it to its billion users to be clear about how the site plans on distributing news .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":167,"left":136,"right":166,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":85,"right":135,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":85,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":109,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":94,"right":108,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":88,"right":93,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":87,"right":5,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":2,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":90,"right":92,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":89,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":91,"right":11,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":96,"right":107,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":12,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":99,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":15,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":16,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":26,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":100,"right":104,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"joi